OL,5,G1750 Come Dine with Me
OL,6,     FHull area. The competition moves
OL,7,     Fto Doncaster, where Tony serves up
OL,8,     Fsome countryside cuisine on a
OL,9,     Ffinal night featuring hit-and-miss
OL,10,     Ffood, dirty cutlery and a
OL,11,     Fwolf-whistling hoo-ha. (Ep5/5)
