OL,9,     FNottinghamshire, where they aim to
OL,10,     Fmake glamping even more glam.
OL,11,G1925 Four in a Bed
OL,12,     FAt Holly Hill Inn, Tom's already
OL,13,     Flet all his competitors know that
OL,14,     Fhe runs the best place in
OL,15,     FRichmond, North Yorkshire. So
OL,16,     Fwhy's he feeling so hard done by
