OL,5,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FBrittany hosts the week's final
OL,7,     Fvisit at Woodland Park Lakes
OL,8,     FHolidays in Windermere, where the
OL,9,     FB&Bers enjoy an arty afternoon.
OL,10,     FBut faces drop when it comes to
OL,11,     Fthe cost.
OL,12,G2030 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FIt's been a fiery week, and every
OL,14,     Flast one of the B&Bers is unhappy
OL,15,     Fwith their feedback. So expect
OL,16,     Fmore fireworks when they meet up
OL,17,     Fonce again to find out who's won.
